    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family! It still smells brand new inside and drives like an absolute dream\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
