    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a museum-quality example of the E46 platform, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS valve timing. It utilizes a Getrag six-speed manual transmission paired with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally perfect with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its original damping characteristics and bushing integrity. Finished in its factory-original paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle undergoes rigorous preventative maintenance, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain and cooling system perform at peak efficiency. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
