      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless deep-gloss finish with professional ceramic coating and zero paint imperfections. The interior remains in showroom state, featuring pristine leather upholstery with no bolster wear, original protective floor mats, and that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; a comprehensive folder of service records documents every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. From the crystal-clear headlight lenses to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in premium rubber, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. Included are both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fit car cover. This is a rare time capsule for the enthusiast who demands perfection.",
